author: xsteve
msg: Added support for user names that include blanks
* trunk/contrib/client-side/psvn/psvn.el:
(svn-user-names-including-blanks): New variable that holds all user names
that include blanks
(svn-pre-parse-status-hook): New hook to allow the modification of the
svn status output before svn-parse-status-result parses the result for psvn
(svn-status-parse-fixup-user-names-including-blanks): New function. It can be
used in the svn-pre-parse-status-hook to convert user names with ' ' to
user names with '-'. That allows user names that contain blanks.

author: dlr
msg: JavaHL: Create an exception class hierarchy.
[ in subversion/bindings/java/javahl/ ]
* src/org/tigris/subversion/javahl/SubversionException.java
A simple base class for all checked Subversion exceptions.
* src/org/tigris/subversion/javahl/NativeException.java
A new base class for JNI-produced exceptions, containing the
previous implementation of ClientException.  Inherits from
SubversionException.  Currently package-private.
* src/org/tigris/subversion/javahl/ClientException.java
Extend NativeException for the majority of our implementation.
